#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to filter the style list using the <guilabel>Search...</"
"guilabel> field above the grid. Moreover, you can use the combo box next to "
"this field to show only the <guimenuitem>Light Themes</guimenuitem>, the "
"<guimenuitem>Dark Themes</guimenuitem> or the <guimenuitem>Color scheme "
"compatible</guimenuitem> themes."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you want to remove a theme, use the "
#| "<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete.png\" "
#| "format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> overlay icon at the "
#| "bottom right of the theme icon. To undo this action click on the "
#| "<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-undo.png\" "
#| "format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon. If you hit "
#| "<guibutton>Apply</guibutton> or <guibutton>OK</guibutton> the themes "
#| "selected for removal are actually deleted, so you cannot undo individual "
#| "or all deletions."
msgid ""
"If you want to remove a style, use the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> overlay icon at the "
"bottom right of the style icon. To undo this action click on the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-undo.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon. If you hit the "
"<guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button the styles selected for removal are "
"actually deleted, so you cannot undo individual or all deletions."
msgstr ""
"Jika kamu ingin menghapus tema, gunakan ikon  "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> yang terhampar di sebelah "
"kanan bawah dari tema ikon. Untuk membatalkan aksi ini klik pada ikon "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-undo.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>. Jika kamu menekan "
"<guibutton>Terapkan</guibutton> atau <guibutton>Oke</guibutton> tema-tema "
"yang dipilih untuk penghapusan benar-benar dihapus, sehingga kamu tidak bisa "
"membatalkan secara individu atau semua penghapusan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the plasma-sdk package is installed on your system, a button appears "
#| "hovering a theme preview and lets you start the <application>Plasma Theme "
#| "Explorer</application>."
msgid ""
"If the plasma-sdk package is installed on your system, a button appears "
"hovering a style preview and lets you start the <application>Plasma Theme "
"Explorer</application>."
msgstr ""
"Jika paket plasma-sdk diinstal pada sistemmu, sebuah tombol muncul melayangi "
"pratinjau tema dan memungkinkan kamu memulai <application>Penjelajah Tema "
"Plasma</application>."

